# raw_data.pkl is intentionally TRACKED: it's a build artifact refreshed daily
# by .github/workflows/refresh-raw-data.yml from a clean IP, so Streamlit Cloud
# (where yfinance is blocked) always serves current model data. Do not git rm it.
!data/raw_data.pkl
